<topic id='business_definition_data_dictionary_change_notice.description'>
  <title>Description</title>
  <titlealts>
    <searchtitle>NHS Business Definition: Data Dictionary Change Notice - Description</searchtitle>
  </titlealts>
  <body>
  <div>
      <p>
A 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_data_dictionary_change_notice">Data Dictionary Change Notice</xref>
 (<xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_data_dictionary_change_notice">DDCN</xref>) is a notice of a change to the NHS Data Model and Dictionary which is not appropriate for 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_data_coordination_board">Data Coordination Board</xref>
 publication as an 
              <xref outputclass="supportingInformation"
               keyref="supporting_definition_information_standards_notice">Information Standards Notice</xref>, as the change does not relate to an individual standard.        </p>
      <p>
The 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_data_dictionary_change_notice">Data Dictionary Change Notices</xref>
 can be downloaded from: 
              <xref href="https://www.datadictionary.nhs.uk/DDCNs/"
               scope="external"
               format="html">Data Dictionary Change Notices</xref>.        </p>
      <p>
Further information on 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_data_dictionary_change_notice">Data Dictionary Change Notices</xref>
 can be found on the 
              <xref outputclass="supportingInformation"
               keyref="supporting_definition_nhs_data_model_and_dictionary_service">NHS Data Model and Dictionary Service</xref>
 part of the 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_nhs_digital">NHS Digital</xref>
 website at: 
              <xref href="https://digital.nhs.uk/media/746/Data-Dictionary-Change-Notice-guidance/pdf/ddcnguide"
               scope="external"
               format="html">Policies: Data Dictionary Change Notice guidance</xref>.        </p>
  </div>
